{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@_NSRange","text":"NSRange","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"range","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCoordinates:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"coords","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger","text":"NSUInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"range","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The range of vertices to replace. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"location","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" field indicates","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the first vertex you are replacing, with ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being the first vertex, ","type":"text"},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"being the second vertex, and so on. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" field indicates the number","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of vertices to replace.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"coords","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of coordinates defining part of the shape. The data in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this array is copied to the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"count","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The number of coordinates from the ","type":"text"},{"code":"coords","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" array to insert in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"place of the coordinates in ","type":"text"},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". The sum of ","type":"text"},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"’s length and this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"count must not exceed the number of items currently in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"coordinates","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the shape is currently visible on the map as an annotation, it is redrawn"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately. If the shape is part of an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object, you must"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"explicitly set the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/shape"},{"type":"text","text":" property in order for any style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layers that use the source to be redrawn."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is greater than the "},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" field of "},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", some vertices will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"effectively be inserted into the shape. On the other hand, if "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is less"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than the "},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" field of "},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", some vertices will effectively be removed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":" extends beyond the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSRangeException"},{"type":"text","text":" is raised. If you want to append new vertices to the shape,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-appendCoordinates:count:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint\/replacecoordinatesinrange:withcoordinates:count:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Replaces the vertices at the given range in the shape with the specified number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of vertices from a given C array."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPoint(im)replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Me